## Typography Sumary 
The Trifect brand relies on the Inter font family to maintain a modern, tech-forward, and clean aesthetic. It is divided into two specific use cases: 

1. Headings Font: Inter Display 

Weights to Use: Regular, Medium, and Bold 

Purpose: Use this for primary titles, section headers, and high-level callouts to give the UI a refined, professional look. 

2. Body Text Font: Inter 
Weights to Use: Regular and Bold 

Purpose: Use this for all standard interface text, descriptions, and functional labels to ensure maximum legibility. 

## UI & App Design Requirements 
When you're creating any kind of UI or app components, these guidelines mandate the following "must-dos": 

Maintain Visual Balance: Use the horizontal logo version (text next to the icon) for standard website headers and documents. Use the vertical version for space-constrained areas like app icons or social profiles. 

Color Contrast & Accessibility: All text and logo elements must have sufficient contrast against the background. 

Color Palette:
Primary: Red (#b11f29): Use for highlights, key interface elements, and the logo.
Background: Dark (#171717): Use as the primary background color to keep layouts clean
Text: White (#dbd6cb): Use for all text in the interface